Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Poco, where in blazes\Nwere you at this hour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:19.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:24.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe,\Nb-but where's Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She went out to look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:32.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She... She went out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Poco, what's the matter?\NYou're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:38.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:42.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:01:00.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Two stars fallen from the heavens
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:08.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Swallowed by waters swirling\Nlight and dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:13.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their ripples move outward,\Npulled toward each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:24.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun will guide the man\Nwho walks the path of honor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:30.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And for the man who follows\Nhis ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...a sacrifice awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:42.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With pounding heart\Nand burning will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With thundering fists
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:49.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And overflowing bravery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:55.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He steps forward, free of doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A fate determined by his blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:22.24,TypeItalic,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 8: Blood Feud - JoJo & Dio
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this lovely flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:33.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your youth is blooming\Njust like this flower is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:36.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Consider this carefully, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:41.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If this flower blooms fully,\Nit will only wither away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A shame, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's sweet sixteen!\NSo pure and innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:54.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how full of delicious\Nlife energy she is, Lord Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:04.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those without manners\Naren't fit to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, mademoiselle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer you a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:14.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you like to enjoy\Nyour youth for all eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:20.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will not force my friendship\Nupon you, unlike some.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are free to choose your own destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:41.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a damned d-devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:08.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Alas. Though you will soon part,\Nallow me to introduce my companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the dreaded Doobie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:18.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since I am not to your taste,\Nyou might enjoy his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:50.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need\Nfor introductions to a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:51.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:52.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Poco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bit you! Bit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's lurking under his mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That zombie is full of snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NVenomous cobras and flesh-eating vipers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:40.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those snakes bit his face,\Nand not just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for Dio's games!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.\NHe squeezed out the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:04.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's learned a lot about blood flow\Nin a very short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:09.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Baron Zeppeli gave\Nhim his life energy before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:17.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use a bit of Hamon to\Nboil the blood of those snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:26.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Poco!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:04.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back from hell, Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still alive, JoJo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:14.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that means\Nyou've defeated my two knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:20.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dio, we await your order\Nto eliminate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:24.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let my fangs\Nmake an impression on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This one I will handle personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to be frank, JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:39.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to have\Nto do this personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We were raised in the same house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NMaking you undead does not please me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I left this business\Nto my knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:55.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:08:02.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you alive makes me realize\NI was too soft of an emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:08.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now I will slaughter you\Nwithout a hint of hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:13.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.\NI'll feel no guilt for killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:19.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to that dapper mustachioed \Ngentleman you were with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did he run off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:26.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, I must express my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThis shames me as a gentleman, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:35.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...truth be told, I, Jonathan Joestar,\Nwill kill you to satisfy my anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:53.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, stand aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:09:00.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have the right to satisfy\Nmy anger first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:06.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeppeli was a companion through\Ntwo decades of harsh training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:11.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, I will send you\Nstraight to the bowels of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:17.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! He has hidden abilities\Nyou don't know about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What an interesting walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:29.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With enough training, humans are able
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto make themselves float on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:38.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in just one night, I have gained\Npower beyond any human guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:47.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat me\Nwith such sleepy movements?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Cross Split Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! By crossing his arms
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,he can attack while keeping his guard up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfect stratagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No fighter has escaped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! Useless! Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's been flash frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:34.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio vaporized the moisture in his body,\Nturning him to ice in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:40.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dire can't send Hamon into Dio\Nunless his blood is flowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:47.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That Dio is truly fearsome!\NHe froze Dire's whole body at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:52.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So feeble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:57.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you would ever\Nbe able to touch me, fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:01.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You came here just to die like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:04.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give them all a good show!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:07.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,- D-Dire!\N- Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the next one\Nto be sent to oblivion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:34.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hamon-filled rose's thorns do sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you scar my face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Speedwagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:53.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:02.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, I've just seen the way\Nto beat your flash freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to send Hamon into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NDire spent his life to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:14.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fill Blueford's sword of luck and\Npluck with Hamon and slice you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:24.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You dare touch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:29.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You dare touch me with your\NHamon filthier than frog urine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've pushed your luck too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:36.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll be a feast for my zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They'll gnaw the faces off your skulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:44.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now he shows his true colors\Nas the worst man in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His cool sophistication is\Nnothing but a cheap mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:56.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he's had a humiliating taste\Nof Hamon, we see his real face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am Pajyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:07.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pluton!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:08.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Barnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Needle Vein Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:22.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roses are living things, so Hamon\Nwill remain inside of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But steel is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to maintain contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is a great horde of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:52.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I can tell, Dio\Nis as swift as a leopard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:57.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Baron Zeppeli,\NJonathan just might keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:05.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Dio is strong enough to\Npulverize flesh and bone with ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:10.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will be decided as they meet\Nin the opening moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:22.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll squeeze the life out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:26.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cleanse the world of your evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:31.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He grabbed some roses\Nwhen I wasn't looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:41.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He circled to Dio's right\Nbecause that eye can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:45.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn! JoJo is a veteran fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He finally defeated Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So feeble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:26.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now you will become\None of my children of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your rubbery\Ncarotid between my fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:39.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So warm and springy.\NWhat a pleasant feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:40.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My legs are frozen, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! Useless! Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy this anguish, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:02.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Move and this delicate\Nblood vessel will snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:12.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open your carotid and exchange\Nyour blood for my vampiric essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-We have to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep those peasants back\Nfor a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:24.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They just won't stop coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:33.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, JoJo, I'll fill you with vampiric\Nessence and make you my slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:39.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you've won, Dio!\NYou've made a fatal mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And how so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:47.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't frozen me completely\Nbecause you are still feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you freeze me, my Hamon will stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut you can't drain my life, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:58.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your tactics are flawed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He put the sword in the flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:07.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That blade is conducting the heat\Nfaster than I can freeze it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon is coming up the blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:18.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sunlight Yellow Overdrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:27.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look again! You can tell that\Nthe Hamon didn't go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My arm is frozen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I only touched his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimated me, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:50.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will admit it.\NI admire your explosive tenacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:56.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I must say that your use of fire\Nwas marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:03.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But JoJo, nothing can escape\Nmy icy grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:06.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a touch on the arm is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can freeze your whole body in\Ntwo seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He squeezed out\Nthe vampiric essence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan hasn't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:28.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you puffed up like that?\NStill looking for a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:34.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you struggle,\Nhuman ability is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:41.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your Hamon training is useless!\NUseless! Useless! Useless! Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:45.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A monkey cannot stand\Nagainst a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:51.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And compared to me,\Nyou are a mere monkey, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:55.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! With enough conviction,\Nhumans can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humans will grow!\NLet me demonstrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:03.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You won't, because\Nyou'll be a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His hand, it's burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His glove is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It just might get through Dio's ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of us will fall in the end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We find out now, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He was blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's breaking through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disintegrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The pain! The burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:13.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My reign...was supposed...\Nto last...for centuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You had to be destroyed, Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He shot his essence from his eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:41.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was centimeters\Nfrom incinerating my brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:47.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The last throes of a demon\Nclinging to life in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio's falling down the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:08.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:23.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's worn out. He should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:26.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's seen too many fatal fights tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:31.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But why would he cry\Nafter killing a bad guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:38.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He spent his youth together with Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:42.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But me? I can smile happily!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:48.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you watching, Baron Zeppeli?\NHe did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:54.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:00.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It may sound like an exaggeration,\Nbut the world is saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:38.48,TypeItalic,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:40.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a joyous occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.74,0:23:42.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These are tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:44.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:47.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:49.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is my new body here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:51.79,TypeItalic,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 9: The Last Hamon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:53.79,TypeItalic,,0000,0000,0000,,
